# Git Submodules Configuration
# 
# This project uses the following submodule:
# - libs/tiny-llm-client: https://github.com/aicorp-cn/tiny-llm-client.git
#
# After the remote submodule repository is created, configure it with:
#   git submodule add https://github.com/aicorp-cn/tiny-llm-client.git libs/tiny-llm-client
#
# For now, tiny-llm-client is included as a regular directory.